{"tid":6259,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一個追求「她」半生的真實故事","createTime":"2016-11-27T09:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T16:05:46.000Z","uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"419d275ab8bfcc28307dd242e4b188fb5f4e84f2","tid":6259,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/171127_a8ca9be740601eff69eb57ef75ec58a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F171127_a8ca9be740601eff69eb57ef75ec58a4.jpg&h=38a4ab08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一站，是幸福？<br />\n<br />\n一個感動人心、真人真事無改編<br />\n追求「她」半生的故事<br />\n一直默默耕耘，一直為她付出<br />\n卻只能在燈火欄柵的遠處<br />\n做她身邊的無名氏<br />\n然後看著她的背影在自己的日記裡漸漸消失...<br />\n<br />\n原曲:交替之間<br />\n主唱:鍾嘉欣、胡鴻鈞<br />\n作曲:葉肇中<br />\n<br />\n處處替她分擔 小雨過得好嗎?<br />\n追半生 我氣力已消散<br />\n遙望 跟妳說著下一站<br />\n期望 幸福的瞬間<br />\n浮沉後跌落凡間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/171207_96972a8494e737020d45b5062f50f9bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F171207_96972a8494e737020d45b5062f50f9bf.jpg&h=19560888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sweetlyricist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsweetlyricist&d=zrSA4My8aCZ8BpN6nxSkGsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=53499190\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sweetlyricist</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: sweetlyricist<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持甜詞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98bd9a380e58a7d5fc1b9853bd4513d382d12b9","tid":6259,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528c0318735a7e39d6274a218859f5a5eec061c9","tid":6259,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB